languages.text: "Инцендия пыталась принести нам закон, и теперь она мертва! Знайте и скажите всем: нет и не будет закона на Футфоле! Никогда!"
"Incendia tried to make us obey her laws, and now she is dead! Know this and spread the word: there is no law on Footfall, and there never will be! Never!"

languages.text: 「インセンディアは我々を自らの法に服従させようと目論んだが、彼女はもう死んだ！この言葉を理解し、そして広めよ。フットフォールには今も、これからも、法など存在しない！絶対にだ！」
languages.original_text: "Incendia tried to make us obey her laws, and now she is dead! Know this and spread the word: there is no law on Footfall, and there never will be! Never!"

languages.text: « Incendia a voulu nous forcer à suivre ses lois, et aujourd'hui, elle est morte ! Retenez bien cette leçon et partagez-la : il n'y a pas de loi à Castel, et il n'y en aura jamais ! Jamais ! »
languages.original_text: "Incendia tried to make us obey her laws, and now she is dead! Know this and spread the word: there is no law on Footfall, and there never will be! Never!"

languages.text: “因森蒂娅打算让咱们遵守她的法律，现在她死了！所有人，把这句话给我传出去：落脚港是个法外之地！以前没有法律，以后也不会有！永远不会！”
languages.original_text: "Incendia tried to make us obey her laws, and now she is dead! Know this and spread the word: there is no law on Footfall, and there never will be! Never!"

languages.text: "Incendia wollte, dass wir ihre Gesetze befolgen, und jetzt ist sie tot! Wisset und verbreitet es: Es gibt kein Gesetz auf Footfall, und es wird auch nie eines geben! Niemals!"
languages.original_text: "Incendia tried to make us obey her laws, and now she is dead! Know this and spread the word: there is no law on Footfall, and there never will be! Never!"

languages.text: «Incendia pretendía que obedeciéramos sus leyes, pero ¡ahora está muerta! Recordad y difundid lo siguiente: ¡En Paso no hay ni nunca habrá ninguna ley! ¡Nunca!».

languages.text: "İncendia, bizi yasalara itaate zorladı. Geberdi gitti! Şunu iyi belleyin, herkese de duyurun: Binliman'da kanun yoktur, asla da olmayacak! Asla!"

traits.locale_text: "Incendia yasalarına uymamızı sağlamaya çalışıyordu, şimdi de geberdi! Bu dediklerimi duymayan kalmasın: Binliman'da hukuk mukuk yoktur, asla da olmayacak! Asla!"
